Now with recent version of Portfolio we can have automatic sync of estimates, but we still need to do an Update from date... to get any changes to the "Remaining estimate". 

In our business we have multiple managers around the globe that work on the same plan. They want to be able to always see the reality of remaining estimates, but currently to see it they have to do an Update from date. But as they cannot do the full update of full plan by themselves, they must be all together in a meeting to do the udpate properly, they never see the real remaining estimate.

Could we have an option to sync the Estimate by also taking into account the changes in remaining estimates?

