When selecting the Stories View of the project timeline it shows all the stages as separates rows. It would be good to have a simple check box to combine these into a single row since all it shows right now is the same issue been worked on at the same time. 3 different colors in the sprint. It would just be nice to see the additional granularity of stories in a nice timeline chart similar to what is seen with the Epics view without the different stages. 

I've attached a screen shot to show what I mean.

